ZH: 我的生活一成不变，每天都是同样的工作和生活。
EN: My life is unchanging, with the same work and routine every day.

ZH: 她的观点一成不变，无论别人怎么劝也不改变。
EN: Her opinion remains unchanged, no matter how others try to persuade her.

ZH: 他的外貌一成不变，仿佛时间未曾留下痕迹。
EN: His appearance is unchanging, as if time has left no trace on him.

ZH: 这件事的结果是一成不变的，不管你做出什么努力都无法改变。
EN: The outcome of this matter is unchanging, no matter how hard you try, it cannot be changed.

ZH: 这个地方的风景一成不变，美丽而宁静。
EN: The scenery of this place remains unchanging, beautiful and serene.

ZH: 这位艺术家的作品风格一成不变，但却留下了深刻的印象。
EN: This artist's style of work remains unchanging, but it leaves a deep impression.

ZH: 我希望我们的友谊能够一成不变，不管时间多长都不会改变。
EN: I hope that our friendship can remain unchanging, no matter how long time passes.

ZH: 这个城市的气候一成不变，四季如春。
EN: The climate of this city remains unchanging, with spring-like weather all year round.

ZH: 这个家族的传统一成不变，代代相传。
EN: The traditions of this family remain unchanging, passed down from generation to generation.

ZH: 这份工作的工资待遇一成不变，没有任何涨幅。
EN: The salary for this job remains unchanging, with no increases.

