EN: This teacher's teaching method remains unchanging, and it is very effective for students.

ZH: 这个游戏的规则一成不变，不会有任何改动。
EN: The rules of this game remain unchanging, with no modifications.

ZH: 我的想法已经一成不变，不打算改变。
EN: My thoughts have become unchanging, I have no intention of changing them.

ZH: 这个组织的目标一成不变，一直致力于环保和可持续发展。
EN: The goals of this organization remain unchanging, always dedicated to environmental protection and sustainable development.

